```python
import sqlite3
import altair as alt
import pandas as pd
```


```python
query = '''
    SELECT name, rank, rating, wins, losses, achievement, ilvl
    FROM battlegrounds, players
    WHERE battlegrounds.url = players.url
'''
con = sqlite3.connect('data/wow.db')
df = pd.read_sql(query, con)
con.close()
df
```
